    {
      "id": "detailed_1_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_1",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and serves as a reliable option for anyone needing a dependable daily commuter. While the mechanical components are sound and the car drives well, the exterior shows its age with various door dings, some fading in the clear coat on the roof, and minor scuffs on the rear bumper. Inside, the upholstery is intact but shows noticeable wear on the driver's seat and some staining on the floor mats. It has been regularly maintained, though it is not a show car; it is a solid, functional vehicle ready for many more miles.",
      "price": 18500.0,
